  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1441458/" class="title-link">阶级斗争观点太浓</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1441458"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/bayernwin/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1251325-18.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/bayernwin/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">geniuschow</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-07-17"
      class="main-meta">2008-07-17 01:12:35</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1441458_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  主要用阶级斗争的观点去评析，偏农民军倾向明显，整体水平不如《南明史》。但要了解明末农民战争全过程，还是推荐必读。当然，我完全理解顾老的苦衷，毕竟成书是在八十年代，如果再过十年的话效果应该会好很多。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1441458/#comments">(15回应)</a>
